
@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <!--ie 相容性設定-->
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1,shrink-to-fit=no">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <title>訪客預約</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css\bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css\jquery-ui.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css\loaders.min.css">

    <script src="js\jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js\popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js\jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js\bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src='js\moment.min.js'></script>
    <script src='js\jquery.validate.min.js'></script>
    <script src='js\additional-methods.min.js'></script>
    <script src="js\booking.js"></script>
    <script src="js\loaders.css.js"></script>


    <style>
        /* 必填 */
        label.xrequired:before {
            content: '* ';
            color: red;
        }

        .loading {
            height: 100%;
            /*100%覆蓋網頁內容, 避免user在loading時進行其他操作*/
            width: 100%;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 99999;
            /*須大於網頁內容*/
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 2;
            background: #666;
            color: #fff;
            opacity: 0.5;
            text-align: center;
        }

        span.jumbotron {
            color: white;
            background-color: #00796b;
        }

        .jumbotron {
            color: #000000;
            background-color: #ffedb7;
        }

        .ex1 {
            padding: 1cm;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="loading" style="display:none">
        <div class="loader-inner ball-pulse"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container" id="headMessage">
        <div class="ex1">
            <h1> <span id="txtHospName" class="font-weight-bold jumbotron mt-3 bg-info text-white" style="font-size:36px; color:white">陪病及訪客登記預約</span></h1>

            <div>
                <p class="lead" style="font-size:20px; color:blue">◎醫院公告訊息</p>
            </div>

            <div class="jumbotron mt-3 bg-info text-white">
                <p class="lead font-weight-bold">預約流程及規範</p>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li>陪病者於病人入院日或更換新的陪病者請於線上登入，並每日護理站回報體溫</li>
                    <br>
                    <li>當天可線上查詢，於到院時出示<strong style="color:red; background-color: rgb(246, 254, 255);">雙證件</strong>：健保卡及身分證或居留證驗證</li>
                </ul>
                <br>
            </div>

            <div class="jumbotron mt-3 bg-info text-white">
                <p class="lead font-weight-bold">陪病規範</p>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">

                    <li>每日固定1次探視時段、每次限1名訪客、每次1小時(加護病房半小時)。</li>
                    <br>
                    <li>住院探病人數每日上限1人，開放上午時段</li>
                </ul>
                <br>
            </div>
            <div class="jumbotron mt-3 bg-info text-white">
                <p class="lead">陪病及訪客登記預約醫院得同意探病之<strong style="color:red; background-color: rgb(246, 254, 255);">例外情形</strong> : </p>
                <ol class="list-unstyled">
                    <li>病人實施手術、侵入性治療等，須由家屬陪同或基於法規需要家屬簽署同意書或文件。</li>
                    <br>
                    <li>急診、加護病房或安寧病房等特殊單位，因應病人病情說明之需要。</li>
                    <br>
                    <li>其他因病患病情惡化或醫療處置需要，或長時間住院病患等情形，經評估有必要探病且經醫療機構同意者。</li>
                </ol>
                <br>

            </div>


            <div class="jumbotron mt-3 bg-info text-white">
                <p class="lead font-weight-bold">❋貼心提醒</p>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li>具居家隔離、居家檢疫或自主健康管理身分者，請多加利用<strong style="text-decoration: underline;">視訊探病</strong>，不得陪病</li>
                    <br>
                    <li>特殊狀況經允許，如無症狀者可進入院區探病，但不得陪病</li>
                    <br>
                    <li>有發燒或呼吸道、腸胃等症狀，不可預約，請多利用視訊與您的家人遠端聯繫</li>
                </ul>
                <br>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a class="btn btn-sm btn-info" href="/STOCC/visit_query" role="button">
                    <strong style="text-decoration: underline;">查詢/取消預約點此&raquo;</strong>
                </a>
                <br>
                <a class="btn btn-sm btn-info" href="/STOCC/visit_query" role="button">
                    <strong style="text-decoration: underline;">@Html.ActionLink("預約探病/陪病點此", "Create")&raquo;</strong>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>